"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        DeriveKey request payloads with different derivation methods.
        """
a = payloads.DeriveKeyRequestPayload(derivation_method=enums.
    DerivationMethod.HASH)
b = payloads.DeriveKeyRequestPayload(derivation_method=enums.
    DerivationMethod.PBKDF2)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
